Class epp_PollRsp

java.lang.Object
  org.openrtk.idl.epprtk.epp_PollRsp
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.omg.CORBA.portable.IDLEntity
public class epp_PollRsp
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.omg.CORBA.portable.IDLEntity

Class that contains the elements used to represent the poll response from the EPP server.

Note usually instantiated by the RTK user, but rather by EPPPoll and retrieved using that class' getResponseData() method.
